---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Summary">
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">IT 11 Unit Summary</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">IT 11 talks about the past, the present, and the future of ICT. It consisted of 7 units, here are the summary for each unit.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Unit 1 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Introduction to ICT</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        This unit tackled an overview on ICT. Also it explored the history of Technology from big computers like UNIVAC to smaller ones like smartphones.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Unit 2 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 5h.01"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Computers in Daily Life</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Different types of computers and uses in daily lives, from personal computers to embedded systems. Students learned binary (1+1=10), flowcharts, and algorithms.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Unit 3 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9-9a9 9 0 019-9"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Internet and World Wide Web</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        History and evolution of internet and Web. Topics included browsers, search engines, and online communication. Tips for safe internet use.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Unit 4 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Information, Control, Ethics</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Ethical use of ICT, data privacy, digital citizenship, and societal impact. Laws and regulations related to ICT in the Philippines.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Unit 5 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.856-1.487M15 10a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 0a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM5 20a3 3 0 015.856-1.487M5 10a2 2 0 110-4 2 2 0 010 4z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Culture and Society</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Impact of technology on culture and society. Digital, media, and information literacy. Role of technology in shaping cultural norms and values.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Unit 6 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Design Principles</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Fundamental principles of design: usability, accessibility, UX. Branding, logo design, color theory, and typography. Creating intuitive digital products.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Unit 7 -->
                <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Trends, Issues, and Challenges</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Current trends, issues, and challenges in ICT. Emerging technologies, cybersecurity threats, digital divide, and future of technology.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
